{"title":"社会主义是天堂，缺少技术不能上！——歌唱农业技术革命的民歌选辑","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义是天堂，缺少技术不能上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——歌唱农业技术革命的民歌选辑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术改革加劲干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义是天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺少技术不能上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了全面大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个必须动脑筋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超卫星越火箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术改革加劲干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南长葛）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万人大会轰连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革命五八年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保守思想焚烧掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革新定实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北红安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚儒乡的程立均，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产跃进好干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚上疮口茶杯大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肿得让人看了怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫说县里开技术会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一跛来县城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别人劝他不要去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说：“不懂技术更痛心。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北红安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽水机，轮子转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽出水来一棚伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能浇地能灌田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙王气的白瞪眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南禹县）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜校改为技术校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天推广好经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党团员带头干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搞不好改革非好汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑子使破心想烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革工作赛过电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南鲁山）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人献一计"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人献一计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三人改工具。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七天改完磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十天改完防霜器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南新郑）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找诸葛，去访将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱乡坚决变个样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记动手，木匠当先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机械化保证能实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南长葛）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打破陈规老经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲、技术要占全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光干不学新技术，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比上县把路弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陕西高陵）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑子想，手磨烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为发明，忘吃饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失败了，重新干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成功了，不自满。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南长葛）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器开动轰轰响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制出新茶味芬香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前用手多疲累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今既快又舒畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水利机器来制茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老幼无人不称夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术工人是哪个？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是社员王春花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（福建福安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良工具家家忙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翁翁响，叮叮噹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良工具家家忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"户户变成小工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人赛过诸葛亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南临汝）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说人力难胜天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁龙抽水上山巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高坡旱地装满水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑的太阳空发癫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州天柱）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业技术大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发明创造干的欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又改犁，又改车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新式农具几百件。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最有效的是手摇磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又省劳力又简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天磨面六百多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两天磨面一千三。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众叫它小钢磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人看见都喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（河南长葛）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推广新农具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老式旧木犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕不深来浪力气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改装新式犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深耕五寸不希奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（江苏常熟）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种机器下了乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姬塬庄上闹嚷嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁链一转轮胎动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"籽种顺着漏斗奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二漏斗齐沿了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次就耧几跷远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡看罢都称赞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠它增产不费难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（陕西定边）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六队决心强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥变了样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连夜来动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工具大改良。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两只双轨道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都表扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"效率大提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增产有保障。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（浙江海盐）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老犁用了几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥脚越犁越浅见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新式犁儿犁进地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老土翻转见青天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（贵州普安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱车子化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"襄阳专区车子化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万条扁担齐放下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推着小车吱吱响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男男女女把歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运输再不压肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人感谢共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（湖北襄阳）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯下筑路条条平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村内家家造新车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献钱，献料，献巧计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两夜造车二百多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东潮安）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一乡实现车子化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息传闻千万家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千乡百里传经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全县社社遍开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（广东潮汕）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}